Setup webstorm with bower and yeoman
  http://blog.jetbrains.com/webstorm/2014/04/using-bower-in-webstorm/
  Now you can create new projects with yeoman
  https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/help/creating-a-project-using-yeoman-generator.html

Open the application in a browser:
  grunt serve

To build the application run:
  grunt build

Test the application:
  grunt test

